Dummy Kotlin:
{code:lang=kotlin}
val v4: Double = 1L {code}
Error is reported: integer does not conform to Double.

Ok, check quick fix menu (Alt+Enter): there is suggestion "Change type to Int".
Apply it: the type is changed to `Int`, but it's still an error.
`Long` type is actually needed.

IDEA 145.1401 + Kotlin plugin 1.0.2-eap-78.
IDEA 162.74 + Kotlin plugin 1.0.3-dev-697.